abstract: Nearly all of top 10 women in tennis are injured or sick heading into Australian Open.
snippet: Almost all of the top 10 women in tennis are injured or have become sick as the Australian Open approaches. Kerber, withdrew from the Sydney International with a stomach illness.
lead_paragraph: Almost all of the top 10 women in tennis are injured or have become sick as the Australian Open approaches. Kerber, withdrew from the Sydney International with a stomach illness.
